            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "1. The musical instrument are never in a good condition .\n2. They don’t allow students to play any instruments .\n3. They have an electric guitar but not a guitar amplifier .\n4. No extra curricular activity related to music (only a singing competition in which they don’t allow to play any instrument).\n5. Doesn’t let student perform on stage .\n6. No holiday on Saturdays for students of class 11th and 12th after knowing that most of them go to coaching (because some teachers don’t teach).\n7. One teacher targets some specific students for no reason .\n8. Very few teachers are good and teach well .\n9. Some teachers can’t even solve a numerical without the help of book.\n10. The management can’t manage anything .\nOnly person who works hard and loved by all is Somra bhaiya.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
